citations:
    citation-asos-bran-ii:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Bran II"
            text_from_source: "When they lost their way, as happened once or twice, they need only wait for a clear cold night when the clouds did not intrude, and look up in the sky for the Ice Dragon."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Bran, Hodor, Meera and Jojen Reed travel north through mountain passes toward the Wall, guided by the Ice Dragon constellation. They shelter with a Liddle mountain clansman. Bran identifies northern mountain clans: Wulls, Harclays, Knotts, Liddles, Norreys, Flints."
